1
00:00:04,200 --> 00:00:05,440
It's so rare that

2
00:00:05,920 --> 00:00:08,240
you can come home early from work to eat with me today.

3
00:00:08,240 --> 00:00:10,500
How long has it been since you ate at home?

4
00:00:11,320 --> 00:00:12,040
Come on, eat.

5
00:00:12,040 --> 00:00:14,100
The vegetables are very fresh today.

6
00:00:14,680 --> 00:00:15,400
Eat more.

7
00:00:16,680 --> 00:00:17,480
You eat too.

8
00:00:17,840 --> 00:00:19,680
Come on, eat.

9
00:00:26,520 --> 00:00:27,780
Why aren't you eating?

10
00:00:30,520 --> 00:00:31,580
I've been exposed.

11
00:00:31,880 --> 00:00:32,560
What?

12
00:00:39,400 --> 00:00:40,200
Who?

13
00:00:41,480 --> 00:00:42,800
It's

14
00:00:42,800 --> 00:00:44,730
the guy who brought me home before,

15
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:47,120
named Li Xuebo.

16
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:53,120
He seems to have found out something.

17
00:00:56,400 --> 00:00:57,860
Then what do you want to do?

18
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:05,880
Eat.

19
00:01:15,320 --> 00:01:16,120
Leave it to me.

20
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:38,560
Officer,

21
00:01:39,360 --> 00:01:40,400
I don't think I've done anything wrong.

22
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,560
Why are you making such a big fuss?

23
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,520
What do you want?

24
00:01:42,520 --> 00:01:43,280
To stop you.

25
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,460
Lin Wei, you can't stop me.

26
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:49,039
Worst comes to worst, I'll retire and quit.

27
00:01:49,039 --> 00:01:50,240
As an ordinary citizen,

28
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:52,440
I can investigate the case myself, right?

29
00:01:52,440 --> 00:01:53,900
Is it any of your business?

30
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,960
I'm not going to argue with you.

31
00:01:55,960 --> 00:01:57,200
I just received a tip

32
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:59,340
that Cao Aiyuan appeared in Dongwan.

33
00:01:59,759 --> 00:02:01,820
Do you want to investigate together?

34
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,240
Everyone is here.

35
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:16,560
Hello.

36
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:17,360
Let me introduce myself.

37
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:20,320
I am Ning Peng, Vice Captain of the Dongwan Criminal Police.

38
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,360
For this operation,

39
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:24,440
I will lead the team to carry out the arrest with you two.

40
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,360
We investigated overnight

41
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,160
and found this.

42
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:28,120
Through the identity information

43
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,800
Cao Aiyuan left at the driving school,

44
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:32,400
we confirmed she is now using the alias Liu Meijuan

45
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:34,160
and working at the Yunting Hotel.

46
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:35,560
We set up surveillance immediately,

47
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:37,560
but the suspect hasn't shown up yet.

48
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,160
Hello, Xuebo.

49
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:59,530
I have something to confess to you.

50
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:03,740
My name is really not Liu Meijuan.

51
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:08,120
I wasn't going to tell you,

52
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,080
but...

53
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,600
I'm pregnant.

54
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:21,960
I'm at home.

55
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,079
Can you come over?

56
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:26,770
I will tell you everything.

57
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:31,600
I'll wait for you.

58
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:47,960
Aiyuan.

59
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:51,160
After we get all this sorted out,

60
00:03:54,079 --> 00:03:55,360
our family of three

61
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:59,040
can live a good life.

62
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,140
Have you two seen this man?

63
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,440
No.

64
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:22,000
He looks familiar.

65
00:04:23,080 --> 00:04:25,280
The day Liu Meijuan came for her interview,

66
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:28,160
a man picked her up on a tricycle.

67
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,840
But that man had long hair.

68
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,280
What kind of tricycle?

69
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:33,600
The motorized kind?

70
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:35,040
Just the most common type.

71
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:37,560
It had some fruits and sugarcane on it.

72
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,440
Are you sure?

73
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:39,240
I'm sure.

74
00:04:40,159 --> 00:04:41,840
Hao, take a few men

75
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:43,360
and check the nearby fruit markets

76
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,760
to see if anyone sells sugarcane.

77
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:45,560
Okay.

78
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:47,920
Who contacted Liu Meijuan the most recently?

79
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:50,200
Recently, it was that customer, Li Xuebo.

80
00:04:50,200 --> 00:04:51,600
Do you have his contact info and address?

81
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:54,080
I have his phone number, but not his address.

82
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,960
But he seemed to be here for a meeting.

83
00:04:55,960 --> 00:04:58,360
Judging by his accent, he should be a local.

84
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,160
Hao, write down the number,

85
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,480
and then take them

86
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:03,680
to find out more about Li Xuebo's situation.

87
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,480
Okay.

88
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:12,040
It seems we have to go to the fruit market by ourselves.

89
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,000
Ma.

90
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:15,760
According to the rules,

91
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:17,800
you cannot participate in an operation while on vacation.

92
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,330
If you want to participate,

93
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,680
remember to report to Captain Li.

94
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:21,640
Alright.

95
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,440
I'll report to Captain Li later.

96
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:24,480
Then let's split up.

97
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:27,280
I'll go to Li Xuebo's house to check the situation.

98
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:04,000
Meijuan.

99
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:07,160
Meijuan, I'm here.

100
00:06:35,440 --> 00:06:36,770
Who are you looking for?

101
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,740
You two, go over there.

102
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:51,040
You two, search that whole area.

103
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:01,840
Ask everyone around here.

104
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,300
Don't miss anyone.

105
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:04,960
We'll go that way.

106
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,640
Hello, sir.

107
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:07,640
I'd like to ask you something.

108
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:09,280
Have you seen this person?

109
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:10,280
Not that I recall.

110
00:07:12,080 --> 00:07:12,880
Hello, boss.

111
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,560
Hello, have you seen this person?

112
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:16,200
And you are?

113
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:17,360
We're from the Dongwan Police.

114
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:19,280
We'd like to ask you a few questions.

115
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:20,610
He looks a bit familiar.

116
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,680
I think he delivered sugarcane to me,

117
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,120
but he had long hair.

118
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:27,290
Then do you know where he lives?

119
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:29,640
It seems to be nearby.

120
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:30,760
Because people in our line of work

121
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:32,240
basically all live nearby.

122
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:32,760
Nearby?

123
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:33,440
Yes.

124
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,480
Around this Chengbei Farmers Market,

125
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,040
there are three places.

126
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:36,760
Caohe Street,

127
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,440
Jinguishan Town and Baoshan Town.

128
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:39,240
For these three areas,

129
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,680
let's focus on investigating them.

130
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:41,680
Thanks for your hard work, brothers.

131
00:07:41,680 --> 00:07:42,240
Okay.

132
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,320
Let me go.

133
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:08,760
Let me go.

134
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,160
Meijuan.

135
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:14,010
What's going on?

136
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,360
Didn't you say

137
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:17,760
you had something to tell me when I came over?

138
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:18,560
Let me go.

139
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,640
You were forced too, right?

140
00:08:20,640 --> 00:08:21,440
Let me go.

141
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:23,560
Meijuan.

142
00:08:27,080 --> 00:08:28,280
What do you want?

143
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,480
This is your home number.

144
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:43,039
What exactly do you want?

145
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:44,840
Call your family

146
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,600
to tell them you're safe

147
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,880
and ask for some money.

148
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,780
My woman and I don't want much.

149
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:51,280
Three hundred thousand.

150
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:53,660
And we'll spare your miserable life.

151
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:55,680
Your woman?

152
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:00,840
What exactly is the relationship between you two?

153
00:09:00,840 --> 00:09:01,680
You lied to me.

154
00:09:05,560 --> 00:09:06,200
Brother.

155
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:09,520
If I give you the three hundred thousand...

156
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:11,450
Then you will let Meijuan and me go.

157
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:22,440
I warn you one more time.

158
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:26,800
Don't call her Liu Meijuan anymore.

159
00:09:34,760 --> 00:09:36,360
Her name is Cao Aiyuan.

160
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,700
You'd better do as he says.

161
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:46,490
You'll suffer less.

162
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,380
Hello, who is this?

163
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:10,480
Son.

164
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,240
I steamed some crabs.

165
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:12,120
Hurry back and eat.

166
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:14,160
Dad, I'm not going home today.

167
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:16,840
Prepare 300,000 for me and leave it at home.

168
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,800
A friend will come pick it up tomorrow.

169
00:10:18,800 --> 00:10:20,880
Just give the money to him then.

170
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,160
What?

171
00:10:23,280 --> 00:10:24,340
Hello? Son, you...

172
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:37,160
Let's call it a day for now.

173
00:10:37,160 --> 00:10:38,690
We don't want to alert them.

174
00:10:39,520 --> 00:10:41,980
Don't worry. Everyone knows this area well.

175
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,720
I'll have a few brothers in plain clothes

176
00:10:43,720 --> 00:10:45,400
guard the only way out of the village.

177
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:47,920
All right, let's come back tomorrow morning.

178
00:10:47,920 --> 00:10:48,560
By the way,

179
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:49,920
what did Li Xuebo say?

180
00:10:49,960 --> 00:10:50,440
Right,

181
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:51,720
he said it himself,

182
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:52,760
he's not going home tonight.

183
00:10:52,760 --> 00:10:53,440
My family said

184
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,300
this is normal.

185
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,120
Okay.

186
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:00,400
Let's go.

187
00:11:10,800 --> 00:11:12,000
It's about time.

188
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,040
I have to go.

189
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:15,960
If I'm not back

190
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:18,040
before dark, you retreat.

191
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:22,200
What about him if I leave?

192
00:11:26,640 --> 00:11:27,300
You decide.

193
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:33,920
I'm leaving.
